; Pipe Name: Three-Wide Labels.pip
; 
; This pipe formats a list of name/adress 
; records so that they can be printed as 
; mailing labels on stock that's three 
; labels wide. Run against "Sample Text.txt".
;
;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;

AppendStr '\e' 
SplitLines 26 51
PadLinesRight ' ' /w25
ColumnOrder 12 3 
JoinLines 3 

